# Build context is the creation-ops repo root. Keep it small: we only need
# ComfyUI/ source, not the venv, models, or sibling projects.

# Everything outside ComfyUI/ — re-include what the build actually reads.
**/*
!ComfyUI/

# Within ComfyUI/, drop runtime state and large binaries.
ComfyUI/.git/
ComfyUI/.github/
ComfyUI/__pycache__/
ComfyUI/**/__pycache__/
ComfyUI/**/*.py[cod]
ComfyUI/models/**
ComfyUI/input/**
ComfyUI/output/**
ComfyUI/temp/**
ComfyUI/user/**
ComfyUI/tests/
ComfyUI/tests-unit/
ComfyUI/.ci/
ComfyUI/alembic_db/

# Keep the placeholder file in input/ so default workflows still resolve.
!ComfyUI/input/example.png

# Custom-node noise: caches, vendored venvs, local data.
ComfyUI/custom_nodes/**/.git/
ComfyUI/custom_nodes/**/__pycache__/
ComfyUI/custom_nodes/**/node_modules/
ComfyUI/custom_nodes/**/*.safetensors
ComfyUI/custom_nodes/**/*.ckpt
ComfyUI/custom_nodes/**/*.pth
ComfyUI/custom_nodes/**/*.bin
ComfyUI/custom_nodes/**/models/**
